{"tid":991024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男用小花狗引誘路邊狗　勒死後吃狗肉","createTime":"2019-01-22T05:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T06:23:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"467358b30663af47ad8317481b982894b4c4b5b4","tid":991024,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"中國福建晉江一名吳姓男子因為喜歡吃狗肉，又捨不得花錢買，居然想出派他的寵物狗，去引誘路邊的狗，把對方騙到偏避處勒死，再把屍體帶回家煮來吃。<br />\n警方表示，吳男是名偷狗、殺狗大盜，自2015年開始，多次犯案。這次因為吃到別人養的狗，案情才會曝光。員警又說，吳男習慣騎著機車，帶著飼養的寵物小花狗外出。路上發現「食材」後，他會讓寵物狗去跟路邊的狗玩，兩狗玩熟了，他會帶寵物狗離開，然後把跟上來的狗誘騙到偏僻處，用繩子勒死，帶回家煮食。吳男坦承，自己平時比較喜歡吃狗肉，為了滿足食欲，才想出用飼養的狗，去「色誘」其他狗。目前吳男已被刑事拘留。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190122/640_e0658b06da7d92684159fda679ef7d18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190122%2F640_e0658b06da7d92684159fda679ef7d18.jpg&h=f538efd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190122/640_556f9c3f29c07cd9ef14f28eba05d903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190122%2F640_556f9c3f29c07cd9ef14f28eba05d903.jpg&h=896d8530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190122/1504942/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190122%2F1504942%2F&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIp5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=39472271\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190122%2F1504942%2F&h=e791e1b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190122/1504942/</a>"},{"pid":"f670e3c4d8348298a16fca7b47910000b243b6a8","tid":991024,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"老納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c0294f62b9858aaaf2ecefb9a5a781aea1443f","tid":991024,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"有養寵物狗但又殺其他狗食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛狗撚點睇？"},{"pid":"00532579cd35af37eb6a37e136a1a1311bf88147","tid":991024,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"小花狗=美斯"},{"pid":"c774d7bdddc97a9890a519ca4782f6d8c84cec76","tid":991024,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f670e3c4d8348298a16fca7b47910000b243b6a8","tid":991024,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"老納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:20:10.000Z","msg":"佢係食定係被食個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e374269970a6a7471cfbf12b81e0c0e45a70c6","tid":991024,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c774d7bdddc97a9890a519ca4782f6d8c84cec76","tid":991024,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f670e3c4d8348298a16fca7b47910000b243b6a8","tid":991024,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"老納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:20:10.000Z","msg":"佢係食定係被食個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"衲dee同類相食"}]}